videos.description: Dewan Huell puts in tricky layup after Davon Reed fights for the ball.
videos.headline: Persistence earns Miami a layup from Huell

videos.description: Jonathan Isaac denies Ja'Quan Newton at the net.
videos.headline: Isaac makes big block to prevent Miami from fast break basket
